00:25:30,220 --> 00:25:32,280
 Molitva za otkriti duhovni poziv.

448
00:25:32,280 --> 00:25:33,900
 Odnosno poziv.

449
00:25:33,940 --> 00:25:35,300
 Ja sam svaki dan

450
00:25:35,300 --> 00:25:36,560
 to molio četiri godine.

451
00:25:36,560 --> 00:25:37,740
 Svaki dan.

452
00:25:37,740 --> 00:25:40,740
 I znate kako sam znao

453
00:25:40,740 --> 00:25:43,500
 da sam ja pozvan na tome?

454
00:25:43,500 --> 00:25:47,260
 Plodove duha svetoga,

455
00:25:47,260 --> 00:25:48,780
 a dva najvačnja ploda su

456
00:25:48,780 --> 00:25:49,940
 mir i radost.

457
00:25:49,940 --> 00:25:53,760
 Pa malo usredućite se na tome.

458
00:25:53,760 --> 00:25:55,160
 Mir i radost.

459
00:25:55,160 --> 00:25:57,560
 Šta ti donosi mir?

460
00:25:57,560 --> 00:26:00,040
 Šta ti donosi radost?

461
00:26:01,240 --> 00:26:02,980
 To ne znači da neće biti teško.

462
00:26:02,980 --> 00:26:04,620
 To ne znači da neće biti strahova.

463
00:26:04,620 --> 00:26:05,700
 Jer ja sam se bojao

464
00:26:05,700 --> 00:26:06,960
 da neću uspjeti

465
00:26:06,960 --> 00:26:08,780
 položiti filozofiju.

466
00:26:08,780 --> 00:26:09,040
 Ne znam.

467
00:26:09,040 --> 00:26:11,380
 Ali ja negdje duboko sam imao

468
00:26:11,380 --> 00:26:12,040
 mir i radost.

469
00:26:12,040 --> 00:26:13,820
 Pa malo o tome razmišljate.

470
00:26:13,820 --> 00:26:15,500
 I nadam se da imate duhovnike

471
00:26:15,500 --> 00:26:16,760
