479
00:26:27,820 --> 00:26:28,460
 Ali kaže,

480
00:26:28,460 --> 00:26:29,080
 ali dondamir,

481
00:26:29,080 --> 00:26:31,060
 ja ne želim učiniti ono što ja hoću,

482
00:26:31,060 --> 00:26:32,100
 nego ono što Bog hoće.

483
00:26:32,100 --> 00:26:32,300
 Rako,

484
00:26:32,300 --> 00:26:33,200
 Bož mi oprosti,

485
00:26:33,200 --> 00:26:34,740
 aj stavi sad Boga sa strane malo.

486
00:26:34,740 --> 00:26:38,780
 Baš ću pristupiti

487
00:26:38,780 --> 00:26:41,100
 po načelu Svetog Augustina.

488
00:26:41,100 --> 00:26:42,360
 A to je jedan

489
00:26:42,360 --> 00:26:43,360
 salazijanac

490
00:26:43,360 --> 00:26:44,200
 meni pomogao

491
00:26:44,200 --> 00:26:45,520
 kad sam bio na duhovnih vježba

492
00:26:45,520 --> 00:26:46,180
 u Njujorku,

493
00:26:46,180 --> 00:26:47,580
 jer ja isto sam imao tu

494
00:26:49,860 --> 00:26:51,740
 nego ono što ti hoćeš.

495
00:26:51,740 --> 00:26:53,700
 Znate što je ovaj svećenik mi pitao?

496
00:26:53,700 --> 00:26:54,120
 Damire,

497
00:26:54,120 --> 00:26:55,340
 šta ti hoćeš?

498
00:26:55,340 --> 00:26:56,920
 Ja kažem,

499
00:26:56,920 --> 00:26:58,320
 ono što Bog hoće.

500
00:26:58,320 --> 00:26:59,120
 Kaže on,

501
00:26:59,120 --> 00:26:59,760
 pust sad Boga.

502
00:26:59,760 --> 00:27:02,080
 Šta ti hoćeš?

503
00:27:02,080 --> 00:27:04,160
 Ja opet,

504
00:27:04,160 --> 00:27:06,020
 ne želim ja ono što ja hoću.

505
00:27:06,020 --> 00:27:06,480
 Ja želim,

506
00:27:06,480 --> 00:27:07,100
 Jerko,

507
00:27:07,100 --> 00:27:08,180
 on pita mene,

508
00:27:08,180 --> 00:27:10,080
 jesi čuo moje pitanje?

509
00:27:10,080 --> 00:27:11,600
 Što želiš ti?

510
00:27:11,600 --> 00:27:14,360
 Ja kažem,

511
00:27:14,360 --> 00:27:14,880
 ba znaš šta?

512
00:27:14,880 --> 00:27:16,720
 Ja želim biti svećenik.

513
00:27:16,720 --> 00:27:19,420
 Ali ja se bojim

514
00:27:19,420 --> 00:27:20,780
 da je to samo moje voljene Bože.

515
00:27:20,780 --> 00:27:21,060
 On kaže,

516
00:27:21,060 --> 00:27:21,580
 polako.

517
00:27:21,580 --> 00:27:22,780
 Kaže,

518
00:27:22,780 --> 00:27:23,140
 Damire,

519
00:27:23,140 --> 00:27:24,600
 jel ti misliš da je Bog protiv tebe?

520
00:27:24,600 --> 00:27:26,440
 Odakle je ta želja tvoja?

521
00:27:26,440 --> 00:27:27,460
 Jel imaš ti braću?

522
00:27:27,460 --> 00:27:28,340
 Imam dva brata.

523
00:27:28,340 --> 00:27:29,280
 Jel oni to žele?

524
00:27:29,280 --> 00:27:30,380
 Jeste jeli isti kruh,

525
00:27:30,380 --> 00:27:31,100
 isti odgoj?

526
00:27:31,100 --> 00:27:31,520
 Je.

527
00:27:31,520 --> 00:27:33,320
 Iako moja mater Mara

528
00:27:33,320 --> 00:27:34,680
 je nas sve tjerla u frate.

529
00:27:34,680 --> 00:27:34,940
 Sve,

530
00:27:34,940 --> 00:27:35,780
 sve u svećenik.

531
00:27:35,780 --> 00:27:37,980
 Sve u svećenik.

532
00:27:37,980 --> 00:27:40,060
 Kaže,

533
00:27:40,060 --> 00:27:40,360
 Damire,

534
00:27:40,360 --> 00:27:41,360
 zašto ti želiš,

535
00:27:41,360 --> 00:27:42,160
 a braća ne žele?

536
00:27:42,160 --> 00:27:44,040
 E,

537
00:27:44,040 --> 00:27:44,520
 pravo.

538
00:27:44,520 --> 00:27:48,300
 Bog je usadio to u tebi.

539
00:27:48,980 --> 00:27:49,540
 Ljudi,

540
00:27:49,540 --> 00:27:51,020
 nije Bog despot,

541
00:27:51,020 --> 00:27:51,480
 neki,

542
00:27:51,480 --> 00:27:52,260
 neki,

543
00:27:52,260 --> 00:27:53,700
 neki tiranin

544
00:27:53,700 --> 00:27:54,620
 koji je protiv tebe.

545
00:27:54,620 --> 00:27:55,740
 Ma čovječ on želi

546
00:27:55,740 --> 00:27:56,580
 da budeš sretan.

547
00:27:56,580 --> 00:27:57,480
 Kaže,

548
00:27:57,480 --> 00:27:57,820
 Isus,

549
00:27:57,820 --> 00:28:00,080
 došao sam da imate život u izobilu

550
00:28:00,080 --> 00:28:01,920
 i da vaša radost bude potpuna.

551
00:28:01,920 --> 00:28:05,520
 Augustin govori o čežnjama.

552
00:28:05,520 --> 00:28:06,940
 Koja je tvoja čežnja?

553
00:28:06,940 --> 00:28:08,320
 Znate koliko je taj svećenik

554
00:28:08,320 --> 00:28:09,000
 meni pomogao.

555
00:28:09,000 --> 00:28:11,600
 Uopće nije bio moj duhovnik,

556
00:28:11,600 --> 00:28:13,300
 nego sam bio na neke duhovne vježbe

557
00:28:13,300 --> 00:28:13,900
 u Njujorku

558
00:28:13,900 --> 00:28:14,860
 kod Salazijanaca

559
00:28:14,860 --> 00:28:16,000
 kao šestestestogodišnjak

560
00:28:16,000 --> 00:28:17,260
 i on je to meni rekao.

561
00:28:17,260 --> 00:28:18,880
 Meni je otvorio oči.

562
00:28:21,880 --> 00:28:23,520
 Je, ja želim biti svećenik.

563
00:28:23,520 --> 00:28:26,440
 Naravno,

564
00:28:26,440 --> 00:28:28,440
 moje želje se mogu pobrkati,

565
00:28:28,440 --> 00:28:29,740
 može se nešto umiješati,

566
00:28:29,740 --> 00:28:31,740
 ali mir i radost

567
00:28:31,740 --> 00:28:32,480
 moraju biti plodove.

568
00:28:32,480 --> 00:28:33,020
 Pa evo,

569
00:28:33,020 --> 00:28:35,380
 malo molim te uzmite to u obzir.

570
00:28:35,380 --> 00:28:37,380
 Jer ja najlazim

571
00:28:37,380 --> 00:28:39,600
 na ogromne probleme

572
00:28:39,600 --> 00:28:40,100
 kod mladi

573
00:28:40,100 --> 00:28:41,340
 da ne znaju šta Bog zove.

574
00:28:41,340 --> 00:28:44,200
 Vajda traže neki znak.

575
00:28:44,200 --> 00:28:45,360
 Jeste vi primijetli

576
00:28:45,360 --> 00:28:47,560
 kako su naša braća i sestre ateisti

577
00:28:47,560 --> 00:28:49,060
 nekad puno sretni od nas?

578
00:28:49,060 --> 00:28:49,760
 Znate zašto?

579
00:28:49,760 --> 00:28:51,100
 Jer Bog njih isto voli.

580
00:28:51,460 --> 00:28:52,520
 Nemojte misliti da Bog njih ne voli.

581
00:28:52,520 --> 00:28:53,200
 Bog njih voli.

582
00:28:53,200 --> 00:28:54,740
 A znate zašto oni pogađaju

583
00:28:54,740 --> 00:28:55,560
 svoje karijere

584
00:28:55,560 --> 00:28:57,220
 i bračni stalež?

585
00:28:57,220 --> 00:28:58,940
 Zato što oni ne traže znakove.

586
00:28:58,940 --> 00:29:00,540
 Oni idu na ono što im je

587
00:29:00,540 --> 00:29:01,520
 Bog prirodno dao,

588
00:29:01,520 --> 00:29:02,480
 intuiciju.

589
00:29:02,480 --> 00:29:07,440
 Oni ne čekaju znak ili glas.

590
00:29:07,440 --> 00:29:10,660
 I svaka im čast.

591
00:29:10,660 --> 00:29:12,880
 Mislim, ja bih volio sve pokrst,

592
00:29:12,880 --> 00:29:14,740
 ali...

593
00:29:14,740 --> 00:29:17,780
 Zato mi katolici nekad imamo

594
00:29:17,780 --> 00:29:19,780
 problem da tražimo znakove

595
00:29:19,780 --> 00:29:21,320
 i tražimo također

596
00:29:21,320 --> 00:29:23,260
 i mnogi od nas smo opterećeni

597
00:29:23,260 --> 00:29:24,640
 takozvani Catholic guilt,

598
00:29:24,640 --> 00:29:25,800
 katolička krivnja.

599
00:29:25,800 --> 00:29:27,040
 Da, ako si svet,

600
00:29:27,040 --> 00:29:28,140
 mora nešto boliti.

601
00:29:28,140 --> 00:29:28,900
 Mora boliti.

602
00:29:28,900 --> 00:29:31,360
 Ne smije biti dobro.

603
00:29:31,360 --> 00:29:32,560
 Mora boliti.

604
00:29:32,560 --> 00:29:32,920
 Ok.

605
00:29:32,920 --> 00:29:34,680
 Ne bježemo od patnje.

606
00:29:36,040 --> 00:29:37,360
 ali vi za vi ovo poziva.

607
00:29:37,360 --> 00:29:39,500
 Jel ti to želiš?

608
00:29:39,500 --> 00:29:42,880
 I jel ti donosi mir i radost?

609
00:29:42,880 --> 00:29:43,940
 Ok.

610
00:29:43,940 --> 00:29:46,820
 Ponavljam drugo.

611
00:29:48,980 --> 00:29:49,600
 Ljudi moji,

612
00:29:49,600 --> 00:29:52,240
 na dan vinčanja,

613
00:29:52,240 --> 00:29:55,560
 kao što sam vam pokazao,

614
00:29:55,560 --> 00:29:56,680
 vi postajete jedno tijelo,

615
00:29:56,680 --> 00:29:57,040
 jedno duk,

616
00:29:57,040 --> 00:29:59,280
 vi postajete vidljivi znak

617
00:29:59,280 --> 00:30:00,140
 nevidljivog Boga.

618
00:30:00,140 --> 00:30:01,520
 Bože, dragi.

619
00:30:02,680 --> 00:30:03,520
 To je ogromno.

620
00:30:03,520 --> 00:30:05,680
 To je ogromno.

621
00:30:05,680 --> 00:30:10,120
 Vi ste hodajući sakraments.

622
00:30:10,120 --> 00:30:12,880
 To je ogromno.

623
00:30:12,880 --> 00:30:17,120
 U tom odnosu vi činite

624
00:30:17,120 --> 00:30:19,680
 najdublju, svetlju stvar.

625
00:30:19,680 --> 00:30:21,080
 Prenosite život.

626
00:30:23,680 --> 00:30:25,880
 A ja u svom svećenstvu

627
00:30:25,880 --> 00:30:29,800
 pretvaram kruhu tijelo Hristovo.

628
00:30:29,800 --> 00:30:32,520
 Ja kad konzumiram svoje svećenstvo,

629
00:30:32,520 --> 00:30:34,380
 dobijem tijelo Hristovo.

630
00:30:34,380 --> 00:30:36,260
 A vi kad konzumirate brak,

631
00:30:36,260 --> 00:30:37,740
 dobijete novi život,

632
00:30:37,740 --> 00:30:38,400
 novo tijelo.

633
00:30:38,400 --> 00:30:40,080
 Ogromno.

634
00:30:40,080 --> 00:30:42,140
 Ogromno.

635
00:30:42,140 --> 00:30:46,340
 Ja ne znam ko to ne bih tijel.

636
00:30:46,340 --> 00:30:49,960
 I Džavao to zna.

637
00:30:49,960 --> 00:30:52,080
 Zato napada svećenstvo,

638
00:30:52,080 --> 00:30:52,660
 mene,

639
00:30:53,680 --> 00:30:56,680
 i zato napada bračne parove.

640
00:30:56,680 --> 00:30:59,760
 Jer on zna tko smo mi.

641
00:30:59,760 --> 00:31:01,760
 I on se toga boji.

642
00:31:01,760 --> 00:31:05,460
 Dakle, poziv,

643
00:31:05,460 --> 00:31:07,820
 postajete sakrament

644
00:31:07,820 --> 00:31:11,840
 i to je vaš put do svetosti.

645
00:31:11,840 --> 00:31:14,760
 Ljudi, zato se ljudi žene.

646
00:31:14,760 --> 00:31:15,620
 Zato.

647
00:31:15,620 --> 00:31:16,300
 Samo zato.

648
00:31:16,300 --> 00:31:18,660
 Samo iz tog razloga.

649
00:31:22,380 --> 00:31:23,680
 Pa ja želim sada,

650
00:31:23,680 --> 00:31:26,720
 imam šest minuta,

651
00:31:26,720 --> 00:31:32,220
 ostaviti vam još jedan savjet

652
00:31:32,220 --> 00:31:36,520
 i ona ću vam postaviti tri pitanja.

653
00:31:38,920 --> 00:31:40,200
 domaću zadoću što vam dati.

654
00:31:40,200 --> 00:31:45,080
 Jedan savjet,

655
00:31:45,080 --> 00:31:46,260
 ja sam već rekao,

656
00:31:46,260 --> 00:31:50,840
 savjet za ulazak u brak,

657
00:31:50,840 --> 00:31:51,740
 prije ulazka u brak

658
00:31:51,740 --> 00:31:53,180
 i ostanak u braku,

659
00:31:53,180 --> 00:31:54,460
 već sam nešto spomenuo,

660
00:31:54,460 --> 00:31:55,580
 ekskluzivnost.

661
00:31:55,580 --> 00:31:56,820
 Daj, molim te,

662
00:31:56,820 --> 00:31:58,140
 uđi u brak

663
00:31:58,140 --> 00:32:00,260
 sa misao,

664
00:32:00,260 --> 00:32:01,780
 ja sam tu za uvijek.

665
00:32:04,320 --> 00:32:04,880
 ekskluzivnost.

666
00:32:04,880 --> 00:32:07,940
 Drugo, vrijeme,

667
00:32:07,940 --> 00:32:08,900
 to sam već rekao,

668
00:32:08,900 --> 00:32:09,560
 i treće,

669
00:32:09,560 --> 00:32:10,280
 žrtva.

670
00:32:10,280 --> 00:32:13,440
 Znate kako znate

671
00:32:13,440 --> 00:32:14,200
 kad neko nekoga

672
00:32:14,200 --> 00:32:15,020
 ili nešto voli

673
00:32:15,020 --> 00:32:16,060
 da se žrtvuje.

674
00:32:16,060 --> 00:32:18,540
 Žrtva.

675
00:32:18,540 --> 00:32:23,540
 Sad prelazim

676
00:32:23,540 --> 00:32:24,480
 na tri pitanja.

677
00:32:28,520 --> 00:32:29,580
 Tri pitanje

678
00:32:29,580 --> 00:32:30,340
 koje ja želim

679
00:32:30,340 --> 00:32:31,640
 da sebi postavite

680
00:32:31,640 --> 00:32:34,080
 prije ulazka u brak,

681
00:32:34,080 --> 00:32:34,820
 pogotovo ako imate

682
00:32:34,820 --> 00:32:35,560
 momka i djevojku

683
00:32:35,560 --> 00:32:36,240
 ili djevojku.

684
00:32:36,240 --> 00:32:39,440
 I ako odgovorite

685
00:32:39,440 --> 00:32:40,400
 afirmativno

686
00:32:40,400 --> 00:32:41,580
 na sva tri pitanje,

687
00:32:41,580 --> 00:32:44,580
 po mom mišljenju

688
00:32:44,580 --> 00:32:45,440
 vi imate uvijete

689
00:32:45,440 --> 00:32:46,300
 za uću u brak.

690
00:32:46,300 --> 00:32:50,500
 Prvo pitanje.

691
00:32:50,500 --> 00:32:51,840
 I pitanje idu

692
00:32:51,840 --> 00:32:53,100
 od lakša do teža.

693
00:32:53,100 --> 00:32:55,680
 Prvo pitanje.

694
00:32:57,440 --> 00:32:58,240
 Možete li vi

695
00:32:58,240 --> 00:32:59,440
 jedni drugima reć

696
00:32:59,440 --> 00:33:01,820
 volim te.

697
00:33:01,820 --> 00:33:04,180
 O, kad ja na zaročnog tečaj

698
00:33:04,180 --> 00:33:04,500
 to radim,

699
00:33:04,500 --> 00:33:05,140
 oni svi strepe

700
00:33:05,140 --> 00:33:06,160
 i odmah kvačica.

701
00:33:06,160 --> 00:33:07,100
 I kač.

702
00:33:07,100 --> 00:33:07,720
 Volim te.

703
00:33:07,720 --> 00:33:08,860
 Volim te.

704
00:33:08,860 --> 00:33:09,880
 Je rekao polako.

705
00:33:09,880 --> 00:33:10,540
 Polako.

706
00:33:10,540 --> 00:33:11,900
 Polako.

707
00:33:11,900 --> 00:33:14,760
 Ali volim te

708
00:33:14,760 --> 00:33:15,880
 u smislu

709
00:33:15,880 --> 00:33:17,480
 kristovski volim te

710
00:33:17,480 --> 00:33:18,960
 u smislu grčke

711
00:33:18,960 --> 00:33:19,320
 riječ

712
00:33:19,320 --> 00:33:20,080
 agape

713
00:33:20,080 --> 00:33:20,900
 što znači

714
00:33:20,900 --> 00:33:22,340
