715
00:33:22,340 --> 00:33:24,000
 a Toma Akvinski

716
00:33:24,000 --> 00:33:25,020
 će reći da je ljubav

717
00:33:25,020 --> 00:33:26,240
 tražiti dobro drugoga.

718
00:33:26,240 --> 00:33:27,300
 Ne sebe, nego drugoga.

