 ukloni svaku tjeskobu,

995
00:40:58,660 --> 00:40:59,620
 svaku sumnju,

996
00:40:59,620 --> 00:41:00,140
 gospodine,

997
00:41:00,140 --> 00:41:01,160
 svaku nevjeru.

998
00:41:01,160 --> 00:41:02,440
 umnoži njihovu vjeru,

999
00:41:02,440 --> 00:41:03,000
 gospodine,

1000
00:41:03,000 --> 00:41:05,180
 i objavi mu svoju volju.

1001
00:41:05,180 --> 00:41:07,060
 Slava Otcu i Sinu

1002
00:41:07,060 --> 00:41:08,240
 i Duhu Svetomu.

1003
00:41:08,240 --> 00:41:10,240
 Kako bi jaši na početku,

1004
00:41:10,240 --> 00:41:12,220
 kako bi sada i vas da,

1005
00:41:12,220 --> 00:41:14,440
 jer vijek je vijek u vam.

1006
00:41:14,440 --> 00:41:16,440
 Sveti Antune,

1007
00:41:16,440 --> 00:41:17,880
 moli za nas.

1008
00:41:17,880 --> 00:41:19,320
 Mario, pomoći se kršćana.

1009
00:41:19,320 --> 00:41:20,380
 Moli za nas.

1010
00:41:20,380 --> 00:41:21,840
 Otca i Sina i Duhu Svetomu.

1011
00:41:21,840 --> 00:41:22,720
 Bog vas blagoslovi.

1012
00:41:22,720 --> 00:41:23,720
 Hvala.

